<section class="hero">
  <div id="hero-canvas" class="hero-canvas"></div>
  <span class="hero-chip hero-chip-1">🔗 <span>DR 74 placement</span> <span class="up">live</span></span>
  <span class="hero-chip hero-chip-2">📈 <span>+38 links</span> <span class="up">this quarter</span></span>
  <span class="hero-chip hero-chip-3">🏆 <span>#1</span> <span class="up">▲ 4 spots</span></span>
  <div class="container hero-center">
    <div class="hero-badge"><span class="spark">✦</span> White-hat link building &amp; SEO</div>
    <h1>Rankings built on <span class="grad-text">real authority</span>,<br>not <span class="grad-text-warm">shortcuts</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Contomatix helps brands grow organic traffic through link building, guest posting, on-page &amp; off-page SEO, and keyword research that actually moves the needle.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a free audit &rarr;</a>
      <a href="/services/link-building" class="btn btn-outline">Explore services</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">6</span><span class="label">Core services</span></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">100%</span><span class="label">White-hat</span></div>
      <div class="hero-stat"><span class="num">24/7</span><span class="label">Support</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-shot">
    <div class="hero-shot-frame">
      <img src="/images/hero-dashboard.svg" alt="SEO dashboard showing organic traffic and keyword rankings going up" width="1200" height="660">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="trust-strip">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="trust-label">Campaigns powered by industry-standard SEO platforms</p>
  </div>
  <div class="marquee" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span>Ahrefs</span><i>◆</i><span>Semrush</span><i>◆</i><span>Moz</span><i>◆</i><span>Google Search Console</span><i>◆</i><span>Majestic</span><i>◆</i><span>Screaming Frog</span><i>◆</i><span>Surfer</span><i>◆</i><span>Google Analytics</span><i>◆</i>
      <span>Ahrefs</span><i>◆</i><span>Semrush</span><i>◆</i><span>Moz</span><i>◆</i><span>Google Search Console</span><i>◆</i><span>Majestic</span><i>◆</i><span>Screaming Frog</span><i>◆</i><span>Surfer</span><i>◆</i><span>Google Analytics</span><i>◆</i>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="services">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">Full SEO strategy</span>
      <h2>One connected strategy — not one-off links</h2>
      <p>Six services that compound with each other: research finds the targets, content and links build the authority, on-page work makes it stick.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-grid">
      <% services.forEach(function(s, i) { %>
        <div class="service-card">
          <span class="service-num">0<%= i + 1 %></span>
          <div class="service-icon">
            <%- include('../partials/icons', { icon: s.icon }) %>
          </div>
          <h3><%= s.title %></h3>
          <p><%= s.summary %></p>
          <ul class="card-points">
            <% s.points.slice(0, 3).forEach(function(pt) { %>
              <li><%= pt %></li>
            <% }); %>
          </ul>
          <a href="/services/<%= s.slug %>">Learn more &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      <% }); %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="features">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="feature-row">
      <div class="feature-media">
        <img src="/images/illus-links.svg" alt="Network of high-authority websites linking to your site" width="760" height="560">
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Link building</span>
        <h3>Links from real sites, with real traffic</h3>
        <p>No link farms, no PBNs. We earn placements on genuine, relevant sites through outreach, guest posts, and niche edits — links search engines actually trust.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Manual outreach to vetted publishers</li>
          <li>DR and traffic checked before every placement</li>
          <li>Anchor text planned around your keyword map</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services/link-building" class="btn btn-outline">How we build links &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-row flip">
      <div class="feature-media">
        <img src="/images/illus-report.svg" alt="Monthly SEO report with growing traffic and goal completions" width="760" height="560">
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Reporting</span>
        <h3>Know exactly what you're paying for</h3>
        <p>Every month you get a plain-English report: the links we built, the keywords that moved, and what's planned next. No smoke, no vanity metrics.</p>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>Live link sheet you can check any time</li>
          <li>Keyword movement tracked against targets</li>
          <li>Clear next-month roadmap in every report</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Get a sample report &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="compare-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">The difference</span>
      <h2>Before vs. with Contomatix</h2>
      <p>Drag the slider — this is what a sustained white-hat campaign does to a site's analytics.</p>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/compare') %>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="process">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
      <h2>A simple, transparent process</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="process-list">
      <div class="process-step"><span class="step-num">01</span><h4>Audit</h4><p>We review your site, backlink profile, and competitors.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="step-num">02</span><h4>Strategy</h4><p>A roadmap prioritized around the keywords and links that matter most.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="step-num">03</span><h4>Execution</h4><p>Outreach, content, and on-page work carried out and tracked.</p></div>
      <div class="process-step"><span class="step-num">04</span><h4>Reporting</h4><p>Monthly reporting so you always know what's working.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats-band">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats-grid">
      <div class="stat-big"><span class="num" data-count="1240">0</span><span class="suffix">+</span><label>Links placed</label></div>
      <div class="stat-big"><span class="num" data-count="180">0</span><span class="suffix">+</span><label>Campaigns delivered</label></div>
      <div class="stat-big"><span class="num" data-count="97">0</span><span class="suffix">%</span><label>Clients retained</label></div>
      <div class="stat-big"><span class="num" data-count="12">0</span><span class="suffix">×</span><label>Avg. traffic growth</label></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">Reviews</span>
      <h2>What clients say</h2>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Placeholder reviews (stock photos) — replace with real client feedback before launch -->
  <div class="review-marquee">
    <div class="review-track">
      <% for (var rep = 0; rep < 2; rep++) { %>
        <% reviews.slice(0, 6).forEach(function(r) { %>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="quote">"<%= r.quote %>"</p>
            <div class="reviewer">
              <img class="reviewer-photo" src="<%= r.photo %>" alt="" width="46" height="46" loading="lazy">
              <span><strong><%= r.name %></strong><em><%= r.role %></em></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="review-marquee">
    <div class="review-track review-track-rev">
      <% for (var rep2 = 0; rep2 < 2; rep2++) { %>
        <% reviews.slice(6, 12).forEach(function(r) { %>
          <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="stars" aria-label="5 out of 5 stars">★★★★★</div>
            <p class="quote">"<%= r.quote %>"</p>
            <div class="reviewer">
              <img class="reviewer-photo" src="<%= r.photo %>" alt="" width="46" height="46" loading="lazy">
              <span><strong><%= r.name %></strong><em><%= r.role %></em></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="faq">
  <div class="container faq-inner">
    <div class="section-head centered">
      <span class="eyebrow">FAQs</span>
      <h2>Questions, answered</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <details>
        <summary>How long until I see results?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>Most sites see meaningful keyword movement within 3–6 months. Link building compounds: early links start the momentum, and rankings accelerate as authority builds. We set realistic milestones in your first-month roadmap.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Are your links white-hat and safe?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>Yes. Every placement is on a real site with real organic traffic, earned through manual outreach. No PBNs, no link farms, no automated schemes — nothing that puts your domain at risk.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>What's the difference between link building and link insertion?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>Link building covers the full strategy — outreach, guest posts, and new placements. Link insertion (niche edits) places your link inside an existing article that already ranks and gets traffic, so authority passes faster. Most campaigns combine both.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Do you guarantee #1 rankings?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>No — and you should be wary of anyone who does. Google's algorithm isn't for sale. What we do guarantee: real links on vetted sites, transparent reporting, and a strategy adjusted monthly based on what the data shows.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I approve sites before links go live?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>Yes. You get the target list with metrics (DR, traffic, niche) before we place anything, and a live link sheet you can check at any time.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How do we get started?<span class="faq-icon"></span></summary>
        <p>Send us your site through the contact form or WhatsApp. We'll run a free audit of your backlink profile and keywords, then send a plan tailored to your niche — no obligation.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-band">
      <span class="cta-orb cta-orb-1"></span>
      <span class="cta-orb cta-orb-2"></span>
      <span class="cta-orb cta-orb-3"></span>
      <h2>Ready to <span class="grad-text">grow your rankings</span>?</h2>
      <p>Tell us about your site and goals — we'll put together a free audit and a plan tailored to your niche.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get a free audit &rarr;</a>
        <a href="https://wa.me/<%= site.whatsappNumber %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-glass">Chat on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
      <p class="cta-note">Free audit · No obligation · Reply within 24 hours</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
